  <brief_title>A Multiple-ascending-dose Study to Evaluate the Safety, Tolerability, and Pharmacokinetics of Pomalidomide (CC-4047) in Healthy Male Subjects</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase 1, Randomized, Double-blind, Placebo Controlled Study to Evaluate the Safety, Tolerability, and Pharmacokinetics of Pomalidomide (CC-4047) Following Multiple Daily Doses in Healthy Male Subjects</official_title>
  <sponsors>
