  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To evaluate the safety, tolerability, and pharmacokinetics of pomalidomide administered
      orally once a day for 5 days, at daily doses of 0.5 mg, 1 mg, or 2 mg.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
